2475&amp;wt.mc_id=aff_BUYAT_2862475&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;impradname=NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;ircid=4272" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>获取剩余门票。</p><p>本月早些时候， <i>NME</i><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">在对《Brat》的四星评论中</a>写道：“在<a href="https://x.com/charli_xcx/status/1761429574490194253">自称的‘俱乐部唱片’</a>中，XCX 提供了纯粹的派对女孩享乐主义。渗透的节拍、急躁的合成器、左场制作和在顽皮的俏皮话或诚实的俏皮话之间穿梭的声线。”</p><p> “通过《Brat》，XCX 证明了走自己的路听起来总是不错，”它补充道。</p><p> <em>NME</em>在对 Sivan 的《Something To Give Each Other》<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/troye-sivan-something-to-give-each-other-lyrics-3513621">给予五星级</a>好评时写道：“最重要的是，这是一张极其重要的流行专辑，充满了爱、欲望、汗水和遗憾。你不需要喝一大杯爆米花就能感到彻底陶醉。” </p><figure id="attachment_3619015" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3619015" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3619015" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Charli-XCX-and-Troye-Sivan.-Credit-Harley-Weir-and-Stuart-Winecoff.jpg" alt="Charli XCX 和 Troye Sivan,.图片来源：Harley Weir 和 Stuart Winecoff" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Charli-XCX-and-Troye-Sivan.-Credit-Harley-Weir-and-Stuart-Winecoff.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Charli-XCX-and-Troye-Sivan.-Credit-Harley-Weir-and-Stuart-Winecoff-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Charli-XCX-and-Troye-Sivan.-Credit-Harley-Weir-and-Stuart-Winecoff-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Charli-XCX-and-Troye-Sivan.-Credit-Harley-Weir-and-Stuart-Winecoff-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Charli-XCX-and-Troye-Sivan.-Credit-Harley-Weir-and-Stuart-Winecoff-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Charli-XCX-and-Troye-Sivan.-Credit-Harley-Weir-and-Stuart-Winecoff-1068x678.jpg 1068w